ining on both tasks of\nrecommendation and KG completion, and the advantage of our model in\nunderstanding user preference. We publish our project at\nhttps://github.com/TaoMiner/joint-kg-recommender.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Feb 2019 10:17:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
